Package: DisulfRisk
Title: Disulfidptosis-Related Weighted DRS Scoring for Expression Cohorts
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("DisulfRisk", "Team", email = "disulfrisk@example.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a small workflow for preparing bulk expression
    matrices and calculating a 20-gene disulfidptosis-related weighted
    DRS (disulfidptosis risk score). The package reads expression files
    from csv, tsv, or txt inputs, validates a bundled coefficient table,
    computes gene-wise z-scores within the input cohort, and returns
    sample-level DRS scores and groups.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
